"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Especially for the proof-of-stake network, a wide distribution of tokens is essential. At present, I think that no network's token distribution is sufficiently decentralized, although Bitcoin and Ethereum are far ahead, and Litecoin is far in third place. It is ridiculous that some new projects are still centralized, such as Solana and Avalanche-I think it is better to trust a reputable bank. Some people may argue that these projects will eventually become decentralized, but there is no practical way to achieve decentralization. Decentralization is contrary to the delegated consensus mechanism (obtaining income through pledges) that they use. The greater the number and types of participants worldwide, the more resilient the network.\\n\\nIn the long run, as Ethereum shifts to the PoS mechanism, Bitcoin's mechanism will become the most decentralized mechanism.\",\"timestamp\":1634225729,\"title\":\"Wide distribution of tokens\"},\"digest\":\"wn4hxRwcPssxN5KJKBtIWjwd8V_KbWZ7z8MY1ErGYa4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x98830d669aE53c947eA158A34e77FeE0CC4C3f01\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"erTqY51qDIeGzd0o5j6jme-UaDssHirk144KYfWKwrY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fz_2dT1uKvE8XvSu2TtndWhmo-4FXAm38t2lPFViSXk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"i8idyz5MefgaNuFcrUbsP7MktGHuhQDZl71gzXNpWf5L_Zf3aqWuUJROxJAzjtmkgUO681flEQfrMrqbyXMVqg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xef9114029ebc856e31ade8514b0c3ec3be0b1133720d98d4c63fdf601ede2bc90693b602571929e7bafd6941ea401730461aa3e54fce7f23d999347bd1392b4f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"erTqY51qDIeGzd0o5j6jme-UaDssHirk144KYfWKwrY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fz_2dT1uKvE8XvSu2TtndWhmo-4FXAm38t2lPFViSXk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"